description:
The Manifestation properties element set consists of properties representing attributes and relationships of the RDA *Manifestation* entity.

Version: 1.0.0

P30001.label: has carrier type
P30001.description: Relates a manifestation to a categorization reflecting the format of the storage medium and housing of a carrier in combination with the type of intermediation device required to view, play, run, etc., the content of a manifestation.

P30002.label: has media type
P30002.description: Relates a manifestation to a categorization reflecting the general type of intermediation device required to view, play, run, etc., the content of a manifestation.

P30003.label: has mode of issuance
P30003.description: Relates a manifestation to a categorization reflecting whether a manifestation is issued in one or more units.

P30004.label: has identifier for manifestation
P30004.description: Relates a manifestation to an appellation of manifestation that consists of a code, number, or other string, usually independent of natural language and social naming conventions, used to identify a manifestation.

P30005.label: has preferred citation
P30005.description: Relates a manifestation to a citation for a manifestation in the form preferred by a creator, publisher, custodian, indexing or abstracting service, etc.

P30006.label: has regional encoding
P30006.description: Relates a manifestation to a designation for one or more regions of the world for which a videodisc or video game carrier has been encoded, indicating that playback is restricted to a device configured to decode it.

P30007.label: has copyright date
P30007.description: Relates a manifestation to a timespan associated with a claim of protection under copyright or a similar regime.

P30008.label: has date of distribution
P30008.description: Relates a manifestation to a timespan during which a published manifestation is distributed.

P30009.label: has date of production
P30009.description: Relates a manifestation to a timespan associated with the inscription, fabrication, construction, etc., of an unpublished manifestation.

P30010.label: has date of manufacture
P30010.description: Relates a manifestation to a timespan associated with the printing, duplicating, casting, etc., of a published manifestation.

P30011.label: has date of publication
P30011.description: Relates a manifestation to a timespan during which a published manifestation is published, released, or issued.

P30012.label: has parallel designation of named revision of edition
P30012.description: Relates a manifestation to a designation of a named revision of an edition in another language or script.

P30013.label: has parallel designation of edition
P30013.description: Relates a manifestation to a designation of edition in another language or script.

P30014.label: has numbering within sequence
P30014.description: Relates a manifestation to a designation that is assigned to a manifestation to identify its position in a sequence of individual parts of a larger manifestation or parts or issues of a larger work.

P30015.label: has numbering within subseries (Deprecated)
P30015.description: Relates a manifestation to a designation of the sequencing of a part or parts within a subseries. (Deprecated)

P30016.label: has electronic reproduction of manifestation
P30016.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation in a digital format that is the result of the transfer of a manifestation in an analog format.

P30017.label: has parallel name of distributor
P30017.description: Relates a manifestation to a name of distributor in another language or script.

P30018.label: has file type
P30018.description: Relates a manifestation to a general type of data content encoded in a computer file.

P30019.label: is facsimile part of
P30019.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that is a part manifestation that exactly reproduces another manifestation.

P30020.label: is part of manifestation
P30020.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that has another manifestation as a discrete component.

P30021.label: has preservation facsimile of manifestation
P30021.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that consists of an exact reproduction on preservation-quality media, such as acid-free permanent or archival paper.

P30022.label: has insert
P30022.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that is a separate part of another manifestation

P30024.label: has equivalent manifestation
P30024.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that embodies the same expression of a work.

P30025.label: is inserted in
P30025.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that includes another manifestation as a separate part.

P30026.label: is also issued as
P30026.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that embodies the same expression of a work in a different format.

P30027.label: is accompanied by manifestation
P30027.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that is issued with another manifestation, without any relationship to its content.

P30028.label: has mirror site
P30028.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that is an exact copy of a website, used to reduce network traffic or improve the availability of the content of the original site.

P30029.label: has digital transfer of manifestation
P30029.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation in a digital format that results from the transfer of a manifestation in another digital format.

P30030.label: has special issue (Deprecated)
P30030.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that consists of a single issue or a supplementary section of a periodical or newspaper devoted to a special subject, with or without serial numbering. (Deprecated)

P30031.label: has facsimile of manifestation
P30031.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that exactly reproduces another manifestation.

P30033.label: has part manifestation
P30033.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that is a discrete component of another manifestation.

P30035.label: is issued with
P30035.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that is issued on the same carrier as a manifestation being described.

P30036.label: is on disc with manifestation
P30036.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that is issued on the same disc with a manifestation being described.

P30037.label: is filmed with manifestation
P30037.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that is issued on the same microform with a manifestation being described.

P30038.label: is reprinted as manifestation
P30038.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that is a reissue of another printed manifestation.

P30039.label: is reproduced as manifestation
P30039.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that reproduces another manifestation.

P30040.label: is digital transfer of manifestation of
P30040.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation in a digital format that is transferred to another digital format.

P30043.label: is reproduction of manifestation of
P30043.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that is used as the basis for a reproduction.

P30045.label: is preservation facsimile of manifestation of
P30045.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that is used as the basis for an exact reproduction on preservation-quality media, such as acid-free permanent or archival paper.

P30046.label: has facsimile part
P30046.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that is exactly reproduced as a part of another manifestation.

P30047.label: is facsimile of manifestation of
P30047.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that is used as the basis for an exact reproduction.

P30048.label: has related manifestation of manifestation
P30048.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation that is associated with a manifestation.

P30049.label: has parallel name of manufacturer
P30049.description: Relates a manifestation to a name of manufacturer in another language or script.

P30050.label: has note on issue, part, or iteration used as basis for identification of manifestation
P30050.description: Relates a manifestation to a note that identifies a part or iteration that is used for the base description of a multiunit or integrating manifestation.

P30051.label: has note on changes in carrier characteristics
P30051.description: Relates a manifestation to a note on manifestation that provides information on variations in the carrier characteristics that are found on manifestations of parts, issues, or iterations of a diachronic work.

P30052.label: has note on distribution statement
P30052.description: Relates a manifestation to a note on manifestation that provides information on the distribution of a manifestation.

P30053.label: has note on manufacture statement
P30053.description: Relates a manifestation to a note on manifestation that provides information on the manufacture of a manifestation.

P30054.label: has note on production statement
P30054.description: Relates a manifestation to a note on manifestation that provides information on the production of a manifestation.

P30055.label: has note on publication statement
P30055.description: Relates a manifestation to a note on manifestation that provides information on the publication of a manifestation.

P30056.label: has note on frequency (Deprecated)
P30056.description: Relates a manifestation to a note providing details on the currency of the contents, on the frequency of release of issues or parts of a serial or the frequency of updates to an integrating resource, or on changes in frequency. (Deprecated)

P30057.label: has note on statement of responsibility
P30057.description: Relates a manifestation to note on manifestation that provides information on an agent, and their function, who is responsible for a work or its expression that is embodied by a manifestation.

P30058.label: has note on series statement
P30058.description: Relates a manifestation to a note on manifestation that provides information on a series with which a manifestation is associated.

P30059.label: has note on copyright date
P30059.description: Relates a manifestation to a note on manifestation that provides information on a copyright date.

P30060.label: has note on dimensions of manifestation
P30060.description: Relates a manifestation to a note on manifestation that provides information on the dimensions of a manifestation.

P30061.label: has note on extent of manifestation
P30061.description: Relates a manifestation to a note on manifestation that provides information on the extent of a manifestation.

P30062.label: has note on numbering of sequence
P30062.description: Relates a manifestation to a note on manifestation that provides information on the range of designators that is used to indicate a sequence of the individual parts or iterations of a manifestation.

P30063.label: has note on title
P30063.description: Relates a manifestation to a note on manifestation that provides information on inaccuracies appearing in titles, complex changes in titles, or on other information relating to a title.

P30064.label: has note on edition statement
P30064.description: Relates a manifestation to a note on manifestation that provides information on an edition of a manifestation.

P30065.label: has publisher number for notated music
P30065.description: Relates a manifestation to an identifier for manifestation other than a plate number for notated music, assigned by a publisher to a manifestation of a notated music expression.

P30066.label: has plate number for notated music
P30066.description: Relates a manifestation to an identifier for manifestation other than a publisher number for notated music, assigned by a publisher to a manifestation of a notated music expression to indicate the printing plate used in the printing process.

P30067.label: has broadcaster agent
P30067.description: Relates a manifestation to an agent who is involved in broadcasting a manifestation to an audience via radio, television, webcast, etc.

P30068.label: has film distributor agent
P30068.description: Relates a manifestation to an agent who is involved in distributing a moving image manifestation to theatres or other distribution channels.

P30069.label: has book designer agent
P30069.description: Relates a manifestation to an agent who is involved in manufacturing a manifestation by being responsible for the entire graphic design of a book, including arrangement of type and illustration, choice of materials, and process used.

P30070.label: has engraver agent
P30070.description: Relates a manifestation to an agent who is involved in manufacturing a manifestation by cutting letters, figures, etc., on a surface such as a wooden or metal plate used for printing.

P30071.label: has braille embosser agent
P30071.description: Relates a manifestation to an agent who is involved in manufacturing a manifestation by embossing braille cells using a stylus, special embossing printer, or other device.

P30072.label: has printmaker agent
P30072.description: Relates a manifestation to an agent who is involved in manufacturing a manifestation by making a relief, intaglio, or planographic printing surface.

P30073.label: has caster agent
P30073.description: Relates a manifestation to an agent who is involved in manufacturing a manifestation by pouring a liquid or molten substance into a mold and leaving it to solidify to take the shape of the mold.

P30074.label: has lithographer agent
P30074.description: Relates a manifestation to an agent who is involved in manufacturing a manifestation by preparing a stone or plate for lithographic printing.

P30075.label: has platemaker agent
P30075.description: Relates a manifestation to an agent who is involved in manufacturing a manifestation by preparing plates used in the production of printed images or text.

P30076.label: has etcher agent
P30076.description: Relates a manifestation to an agent who is involved in manufacturing a manifestation by subjecting metal, glass, or some other surface used for printing, to acid or another corrosive substance.

P30077.label: has collotyper agent
P30077.description: Relates a manifestation to an agent who is involved in manufacturing a manifestation by using a photomechanical process for making prints directly from a hardened film of gelatin or other colloid that has ink-receptive and ink-repellent surfaces.

P30078.label: has printer agent
P30078.description: Relates a manifestation to an agent who is involved in manufacturing a manifestation of printed text, notated music, etc., from type or plates, such as a book, newspaper, magazine, broadside, score, etc.

P30079.label: has other agent associated with manifestation (Deprecated)
P30079.description: Relates a manifestation to an agent other than a producer, publisher, distributor, or manufacturer who is associated with a manifestation. (Deprecated)

P30080.label: has distributor agent
P30080.description: Relates a manifestation to an agent who is responsible for distributing a manifestation.

P30081.label: has producer agent of unpublished manifestation
P30081.description: Relates a manifestation to an agent who is responsible for inscribing, fabricating, constructing, etc., an unpublished manifestation.

P30082.label: has manufacturer agent
P30082.description: Relates a manifestation to an agent who is responsible for printing, duplicating, casting, etc., a published manifestation.

P30083.label: has publisher agent
P30083.description: Relates a manifestation to an agent who is responsible for publishing, releasing, or issuing a manifestation.

P30084.label: has applied material
P30084.description: Relates a manifestation to a physical or chemical substance applied to a base material of a manifestation.

P30085.label: has place of distribution
P30085.description: Relates a manifestation to a place associated with the distribution of a published manifestation.

P30086.label: has place of production
P30086.description: Relates a manifestation to a place associated with the inscription, fabrication, construction, etc., of an unpublished manifestation.

P30087.label: has place of manufacture
P30087.description: Relates a manifestation to a place associated with the printing, duplicating, casting, etc., of a published manifestation.

P30088.label: has place of publication
P30088.description: Relates a manifestation to a place associated with the publication, release, or issuing of a published manifestation.

P30089.label: has parallel place of distribution
P30089.description: Relates a manifestation to a place of distribution in another language or script.

P30090.label: has parallel place of manufacture
P30090.description: Relates a manifestation to a place of manufacture in another language or script.

P30091.label: has parallel place of production
P30091.description: Relates a manifestation to a place of production in another language or script.

P30092.label: has parallel place of publication
P30092.description: Relates a manifestation to a place of publication in another language or script.

P30093.label: is reprint of manifestation of
P30093.description: Relates a manifestation to a printed manifestation that is used as the basis for a reissue of a manifestation.

P30094.label: has parallel name of producer
P30094.description: Relates a manifestation to a name of producer in another language or script.

P30095.label: has parallel name of publisher
P30095.description: Relates a manifestation to a name of publisher in another language or script.

P30096.label: has encoding format
P30096.description: Relates a manifestation to a schema, standard, etc., that is used to encode the digital content of a manifestation.

P30097.label: has first alphanumeric designation of alternative sequence
P30097.description: Relates a manifestation to a designation in the form of numbers or alphabetic characters that is used to indicate the first in a concurrent sequence of numbering of the parts or iterations of a manifestation.

P30098.label: has last alphanumeric designation of alternative sequence
P30098.description: Relates a manifestation to a designation in the form of numbers or alphabetic characters that is used to indicate the last in a concurrent sequence of numbering of the parts or iterations of a manifestation.

P30099.label: has first chronological designation of alternative sequence
P30099.description: Relates a manifestation to a designation in the form of a date or other timespan that is used to indicate the first in a concurrent sequence of numbering of the parts or iterations of a manifestation.

P30100.label: has last chronological designation of alternative sequence
P30100.description: Relates a manifestation to a designation in the form of a date or other timespan that is used to indicate the last in a concurrent sequence of numbering of the parts or iterations of a manifestation.

P30101.label: is special issue of (Deprecated)
P30101.description: Relates a manifestation to a periodical or newspaper containing a single issue or a supplementary section devoted to a special subject, with or without serial numbering. (Deprecated)

P30102.label: has digital representation of cartographic content
P30102.description: Relates a manifestation to a set of technical details relating to the encoding of geospatial information in a manifestation.

P30103.label: has exemplar of manifestation
P30103.description: Relates a manifestation to an item that is a single instance of a manifestation.

P30104.label: has video format
P30104.description: Relates a manifestation to a standard, etc., used to encode the analog video content of a manifestation.

P30105.label: has statement of responsibility relating to title proper
P30105.description: Relates a manifestation to a statement of responsibility that is associated with a title proper.

P30106.label: has series statement
P30106.description: Relates a manifestation to a statement that identifies a series and a numbering within series that is associated with a manifestation.

P30107.label: has edition statement
P30107.description: Relates a manifestation to a statement that identifies an edition to which a manifestation belongs.

P30108.label: has distribution statement
P30108.description: Relates a manifestation to a statement that identifies a place of distribution, a distributor, and a date of distribution of a published manifestation.

P30109.label: has manufacture statement
P30109.description: Relates a manifestation to a statement that identifies a place or places of manufacture, manufacturer or manufacturers, and date or dates of manufacture of a published manifestation.

P30110.label: has production statement
P30110.description: Relates a manifestation to a statement that identifies a place or places of production, producer or producers, and date or dates of production of an unpublished manifestation.

P30111.label: has publication statement
P30111.description: Relates a manifestation to a statement that identifies a place or places of publication, publisher or publishers, and date or dates of publication of a manifestation.

P30112.label: has parallel statement of responsibility relating to named revision of edition
P30112.description: Relates a manifestation to a statement of responsibility relating to named revision of an edition in another language or script.

P30113.label: has parallel statement of responsibility relating to series
P30113.description: Relates a manifestation to a statement of responsibility relating to series in another language or script.

P30114.label: has parallel statement of responsibility relating to subseries (Deprecated)
P30114.description: Relates a manifestation to a statement of responsibility relating to subseries in another language or script. (Deprecated)

P30115.label: has parallel statement of responsibility relating to edition
P30115.description: Relates a manifestation to a statement of responsibility relating to the edition in another language or script.

P30116.label: has parallel statement of responsibility relating to title proper
P30116.description: Relates a manifestation to a statement of responsibility relating to title proper in another language or script.

P30117.label: has statement of responsibility
P30117.description: Relates a manifestation to a statement that identifies, and indicates the function of, an agent who is responsible for a work or its expression that is embodied by a manifestation.

P30118.label: has statement of responsibility relating to named revision of edition
P30118.description: Relates a manifestation to a statement of responsibility that is associated with a named revision of an edition.

P30119.label: has statement of responsibility relating to series
P30119.description: Relates a manifestation to a statement of responsibility that is associated with a series.

P30120.label: has statement of responsibility relating to subseries (Deprecated)
P30120.description: Relates a manifestation to a statement relating to the identification of agents responsible for a subseries. (Deprecated)

P30121.label: has statement of responsibility relating to edition
P30121.description: Relates a manifestation to a statement of responsibility that is associated with an edition.

P30122.label: has emulsion on microfilm and microfiche
P30122.description: Relates a manifestation to a suspension of light-sensitive chemicals that is used as a coating on a microfilm or microfiche.

P30123.label: has broadcast standard
P30123.description: Relates a manifestation to a system used to format a manifestation of a video for television broadcast.

P30124.label: has digital file characteristic
P30124.description: Relates a manifestation to a technical specification relating to the digital encoding of text, image, audio, video, and other types of data in a manifestation.

P30125.label: has sound characteristic
P30125.description: Relates a manifestation to a technical specification relating to the encoding of sound in a manifestation.

P30126.label: has video characteristic
P30126.description: Relates a manifestation to a technical specification relating to the encoding of video images in a manifestation.

P30127.label: has projection characteristic of motion picture film
P30127.description: Relates a manifestation to a technical specification relating to the projection of a motion picture film.

P30128.label: has variant title of manifestation
P30128.description: Relates a manifestation to a title of manifestation that is not selected for preference in a specific application or context

P30129.label: has later title proper (Deprecated)
P30129.description: Relates a manifestation to a title proper appearing on a later issue or part of a multipart monograph or serial that differs from that on the first or earliest issue or part. (Deprecated)

P30130.label: has earlier title proper (Deprecated)
P30130.description: Relates a manifestation to a title proper appearing on an earlier iteration of an integrating resource that differs from that on the current iteration. (Deprecated)

P30131.label: has abbreviated title
P30131.description: Relates a manifestation to a title that has been abbreviated for purposes of indexing or identification.

P30132.label: has designation of named revision of edition
P30132.description: Relates a manifestation to a word, character, or group of words or characters, that identifies a particular revision of a named edition.

P30133.label: has designation of edition
P30133.description: Relates a manifestation to a word, character, or group of words or characters, that identifies an edition to which a manifestation belongs.

P30134.label: has title of manifestation
P30134.description: Relates a manifestation to an appellation of manifestation in natural language and phrasing used in common discourse.

P30135.label: has work manifested
P30135.description: Relates a manifestation to a work that is embodied by a manifestation.

P30136.label: is electronic reproduction of manifestation of
P30136.description: Relates a manifestation to a manifestation in an analog format that is transferred to a digital format.

P30137.label: has note on manifestation
P30137.description: Relates a manifestation to a broad unstructured description of one or more attributes of a manifestation.

P30138.label: has special playback characteristic
P30138.description: Relates a manifestation to an equalization system, noise-reduction system, etc., used in making an audio recording.

P30139.label: has expression manifested
P30139.description: Relates a manifestation to an expression that is embodied by a manifestation.

P30140.label: has related item of manifestation
P30140.description: Relates a manifestation to an item that is associated with a manifestation.

P30141.label: has contact information
P30141.description: Relates a manifestation to a name, address, etc., of an agent from which a manifestation may be obtained.

P30142.label: has other title information
P30142.description: Relates a manifestation to a word, character, or group of words or characters that appears in conjunction with, and is subordinate to, a title proper of a manifestation.

P30143.label: has other title information of series
P30143.description: Relates a manifestation to a word, character, or group of words or characters that appears in conjunction with, and is subordinate to, a title of series.

P30144.label: has other title information of subseries (Deprecated)
P30144.description: Relates a manifestation to a word, character, or group of words or characters that appears in conjunction with, and is subordinate to, a title proper of a subseries. (Deprecated)

P30145.label: has restriction on access to manifestation
P30145.description: Relates a manifestation to a limitation placed on access to a manifestation.

P30146.label: has restriction on use of manifestation
P30146.description: Relates a manifestation to a limitation placed on reproduction, publication, exhibition, etc., of a manifestation.

P30147.label: has first alphanumeric designation of sequence
P30147.description: Relates a manifestation to a designation in the form of numbers or alphabetic characters that is used to indicate the first in a sequence of numbering of the parts or iterations of a manifestation.

P30148.label: has last alphanumeric designation of sequence
P30148.description: Relates a manifestation to a designation in the form of numbers or alphabetic characters that is used to indicate the last in a sequence of numbering of the parts or iterations of a manifestation.

P30149.label: has first chronological designation of sequence
P30149.description: Relates a manifestation to a designation in the form of a date or other timespan that is used to indicate the first in a sequence of numbering of the parts or iterations of a manifestation.

P30150.label: has last chronological designation of sequence
P30150.description: Relates a manifestation to a designation in the form of a date or other timespan that is used to indicate the last in a sequence of numbering of the parts or iterations of a manifestation.

P30151.label: has parallel other title information
P30151.description: Relates a manifestation to an other title information in another language or script.

P30152.label: has parallel other title information of series
P30152.description: Relates a manifestation to an other title information of series in another language or script.

P30153.label: has parallel other title information of subseries (Deprecated)
P30153.description: Relates a manifestation to an other title information of a subseries in another language or script. (Deprecated)

P30154.label: has uniform resource locator
P30154.description: Relates a manifestation to an address of an online resource.

P30155.label: has layout
P30155.description: Relates a manifestation to an arrangement of text, images, tactile notation, etc., in a manifestation.

P30156.label: has title proper
P30156.description: Relates a manifestation to title of manifestation that is selected for preference in a specific application or context.

P30157.label: has title of series
P30157.description: Relates a manifestation to a title that identifies a series to which a manifestation belongs.

P30158.label: has title proper of subseries (Deprecated)
P30158.description: Relates a manifestation to a name of a series appearing on a manifestation of an issue of a subseries. (Deprecated)

P30159.label: has resolution
P30159.description: Relates a manifestation to a clarity or fineness of detail in a digital image, expressed by the measurement of the image in pixels, etc.

P30160.label: has term of availability
P30160.description: Relates a manifestation to a condition under which the publisher, distributor, etc., will normally supply a manifestation or the price of a manifestation.

P30161.label: has track configuration
P30161.description: Relates a manifestation to a configuration of the audio track on a soundtrack film.

P30162.label: has equipment or system requirement
P30162.description: Relates a manifestation to a system or equipment required for use, playback, etc., of an electronic analog or digital manifestation.

P30163.label: has presentation format
P30163.description: Relates a manifestation to a format used in the production of a projected image.

P30164.label: has groove characteristic
P30164.description: Relates a manifestation to a groove width of an analog disc or a groove pitch of an analog cylinder.

P30165.label: has numbering of sequence
P30165.description: Relates a manifestation to the first and last designations of a sequence of manifestations of the individual parts or iterations of a manifestation.

P30166.label: has ISSN of series (Deprecated)
P30166.description: Relates a manifestation to an identifier for manifestation that is assigned to a series by an ISSN registration agency. (Deprecated)

P30167.label: has ISSN of subseries (Deprecated)
P30167.description: Relates a manifestation to an identifier for manifestation that is assigned to a subseries by an ISSN registration agency. (Deprecated)

P30168.label: has frequency (Deprecated)
P30168.description: Relates a manifestation to an interval at which an issue or part of a serial or an update to an integrating resource is issued. (Deprecated)

P30169.label: has dimensions
P30169.description: Relates a manifestation to a measurement of a carrier or a container of a manifestation.

P30170.label: has dimensions of cartographic image
P30170.description: Relates a manifestation to a measurement of a face of a map or cartographic diagram, view, profile, or section.

P30171.label: has dimensions of still image
P30171.description: Relates a manifestation to a measurement of the pictorial area of a still image.

P30172.label: has type of recording
P30172.description: Relates a manifestation to a method used to encode audio content for playback.

P30173.label: has name of distributor
P30173.description: Relates a manifestation to a name of an agent who is responsible for distributing a published manifestation.

P30174.label: has name of producer
P30174.description: Relates a manifestation to a name of an agent who is responsible for inscribing, fabricating, constructing, etc., an unpublished manifestation.

P30175.label: has name of manufacturer
P30175.description: Relates a manifestation to a name of an agent who is responsible for printing, duplicating, casting, etc., a published manifestation.

P30176.label: has name of publisher
P30176.description: Relates a manifestation to a name of an agent who is responsible for publishing a manifestation.

P30182.label: has extent of manifestation
P30182.description: Relates a manifestation to a number and type of unit or subunit of a manifestation.

P30183.label: has file size
P30183.description: Relates a manifestation to a number of bytes in a digital file.

P30184.label: has configuration of playback channels
P30184.description: Relates a manifestation to a number of sound channels used to make a recording.

P30185.label: has tape configuration
P30185.description: Relates a manifestation to a number of tracks on an audiotape.

P30186.label: has mount
P30186.description: Relates a manifestation to a physical material used for the support or backing to which the base material of a manifestation has been attached.

P30187.label: has production method
P30187.description: Relates a manifestation to a process used to produce a manifestation.

P30189.description: Relates a manifestation to the process used to produce an original manuscript or a copy.

P30191.label: has generation
P30191.description: Relates a manifestation to a relationship between an original carrier and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original.

P30196.label: has polarity
P30196.description: Relates a manifestation to a relationship of the colours and tones in an image to the colours and tones of the object reproduced.

P30197.label: has bibliographic format
